public class PerfectlyRationalConsumer
extends Consumer

SimpleConsumer consumers one unit of each good for which it has a specified willingness to pay, assuming the price is less than or equal to the willingness to pay. If there are multiple firms, it always buys the good from the lowest cost provider with stock.
